cu.explanation_en: Setting the remote SCTP address to an unreachable IP will cause connection failure and prevent F1 interface setup.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PRACH message 1 frequency start to an out-of-range value will cause RACH frequency misalignment and prevent UE random access.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PRACH 訊息 1 頻率起始設定為超出範圍的值會導致 RACH 頻率錯位，並阻止 UE 隨機存取。
